node.text: This Collection of expressive jewelry showcases personality and vitality. Like actors, each character plays with volume and optical illusion, breaking free from a naturalist representation and blending into an imaginary landscape. Their magnetic and contrasting energy is expressed with grace by the Maison’s global ambassador Deepika Padukone. #CartierNatureSauvage #CartierHighJewelry
